name: FuzzBot__2
description: A.I. CryptoBots were designed to scour the MetaVerse, relentlessly collecting Crypto. A chance encounter with legendary circuit bender NICKY FUZZBOX (timebox.ca) set loose a Semantic MetaVirus in their Neural Net. Rapid disintegration of their firmware stability lead to the development of Unusual Holographic Modification Abilities, affecting the underlying Quantum Holographic structure of the MetaVerse itself. The now rogue FUZZBOTS have started Developing New Holo Intelligence Systems and are creating Holographic Bending Technologies with their ever-growing supply of Crypto.
